-- ABB, RWE Investigating Technology for Electric Car Charging
-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 2012-02-06T09:05:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/abb-rwe-investigating-technology-for-electric-car-charging.html
  ABB Ltd. (ABBN)  and  RWE AG (RWE)  have agreed to
investigate a combined technology offering for networked
charging infrastructure for electric vehicles, ABB said today in
an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Verschuur at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net  